* Solar_App_Hello::$layout_link -- An array of <link> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Hello::$layout_meta -- An array of <meta> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Hello::$layout_object -- An array of <object> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Hello::$layout_right -- An array of content for the layout <div id="right"> block.

* Solar_App_Hello::$layout_script -- An array of <script> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Hello::$layout_style -- An array of <style> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Hello::$layout_title -- The <title> tag value for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Hello::$layout_top -- An array of content for the layout <div id="top"> block.

* Solar_App_Hello::$list -- The list of available locale codes.

* Solar_App_Hello::$text -- The translated text.

++ Protected

* Solar_App_Hello::$_action -- The action being requested of (performed by) the application.

